summary: Hate bare areas with no life? Downloading this mod adds more plants and foliage to Whiterun.
descriptionHtml:
Whiterun is completely re-done with more trees/bushes/grasses/plants etc.

Mod should be compatible with any other mods, if not please tell me, thanks.

Any bugs found, report to me and ill fix immediately.

My first mod guys, I am learning quick... - PLEASE COMMENT and tell me if it works.

Latest version: 1.0 - Keep upto date - Check out riften too!
author: Swordy083
